    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Sky Combat》是一款快节奏的二战航空游戏，你将驾驶标志性的战斗机冲向终点。使用机关枪、导弹和加速器等道具，在刺激的空战中超越对手。胜负取决于速度与策略！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225030/extras/9aa30e9e2ba54834ec4a784035d213e8.webp?t=1772360454\" width=612 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225030/extras/bdef20adf3d1ae1c27967142b32733d7.poster.avif?t=1772360454\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225030/extras/bdef20adf3d1ae1c27967142b32733d7.webm?t=1772360454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225030/extras/bdef20adf3d1ae1c27967142b32733d7.mp4?t=1772360454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 Sky Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Sky Combat》带来令人兴奋的二战空战体验，高速的空中格斗与惊险的竞速尽在其中。在单人模式下，你可以参加锦标赛、街机竞速或计时赛，场景设定在标志性的二战战场上空。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225030/extras/86797cfeb2704e767b89f2d9236a5eab.webp?t=1772360454\" width=612 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225030/extras/d97810628c5112f812cb3e42656df84d.poster.avif?t=1772360454\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225030/extras/d97810628c5112f812cb3e42656df84d.webm?t=1772360454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225030/extras/d97810628c5112f812cb3e42656df84d.mp4?t=1772360454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Sky Combat》中操控来自美国、德国、英国和日本的传奇战机，体验充满混乱与激情的高速空战。使用机关枪、导弹和加速器来获取优势，抢先冲过终点线。通过本地合作模式，挑战好友，参与锦标赛或街机竞速，感受充满标志性战机与激烈对战的多人体验。</p>",
